Radio and TV personality Stella Katiwa, popularly known as Miss Katiwa, has said 'Yes' to a marriage proposal by Harambee Stars goalkeeper Arnold Origi. Speaking about the couple, a source told Word Is yesterday a photo of the two together posted during the holidays was taken after their traditional wedding. “That photo was taken in shags, when the couple had gone for the introduction ceremony. This extended to them sharing Christmas Day together,” the source said. Adding, “Origi and Miss Katiwa now live together in a posh apartment on State House Road. Tunangoja tu wedding.” Over the weekend, Miss Katiwa shared photos of her engagement ring on social media, and the couple are rumoured to be planning to relocate abroad.